                     <title xml:lang="en">An anthology of poetry.</title>
                     <note>The text ends with f71, breaking off abruptly (unless the folios are bound out of order). This is followed by three folios in the same format and hand containing an index of the first phrases of the poems, not carried right through. After this are two folios with poems of Jamal al-Din Bukhari and his son Kamal al-Din. F1a: signature of David Price. On European paper. Includes poems by Bu 'Ali Qalandar, Nargisi, Rindi, Jami, Sa'ib, Ibn Yamin, Kalim, 'Urfi, et al. with a mathnawi by Nasir 'Ali. Headings and page numbers in red. Compiler not named.</note>
                     <incipit>Gar 'ishq nabudi wa gham-i 'ishq nabudi.</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian.</textLang>
